properties.areaDesc: Eastern Sierra Slopes of Inyo County
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 13 at 3:26AM PST until January 14 at 4:00PM PST by NWS Las Vegas NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 65 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Eastern Sierra Slopes.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 4 PM PST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Winds could blow down tree limbs and loft unsecured
objects. A few power outages are possible. Travel in the eastern
Sierra could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 PM PST TUESDAY
